*** 東非河馬 ''Hippopotamus amphibius kiboko
*** 西非河馬 ''Hippopotamus amphibius tschadensis
** [[灭绝|†]][[歐洲河馬|歐洲河馬]] ''Hippopotamus antiquus''
** [[灭绝|†]][[比蒙河馬|比蒙河馬]] ''Hippopotamus behemoth''
** [[灭绝|†]][[克里特侏儒河馬|克里特侏儒河馬]] ''Hippopotamus creutzburgi''
*** [[灭绝|†]]''Hippopotamus creutzburgi creutzburgi''
*** [[灭绝|†]]''Hippopotamus creutzburgi parvus''
